---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Claude Code Workflow Studio - Project background, purpose, and key features"
>
  <style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--brand-color) 0%,
      var(--brand-color-dark) 100%
    );
    color: white;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    margin: 0;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section {
    background: var(--color-panel);
    padding: 40px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--gray-12);
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--brand-color);
    padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .content-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-12);
  }

  .content-section p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-11);
  }

  .content-section ul {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }

  .content-section li {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-11);
  }

  .content-section strong {
    color: var(--brand-color);
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }

  .feature-item {
    background: var(--gray-2);
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-color);
  }

  .feature-item h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--gray-12);
  }

  .feature-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--gray-11);
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--brand-color) 0%,
      var(--brand-color-dark) 100%
    );
    color: white;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: white;
    color: var(--brand-color);
    padding: 15px 40px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s,
      box-shadow 0.3s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-section {
      padding: 25px;
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  </style>

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Claude Code Workflow Studio</h1>
      <p>
        An AI-powered next-generation development workflow automation platform
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>About the Project</h2>
      <p>
        Claude Code Workflow Studio is a development workflow automation
        platform leveraging Anthropic's Claude AI. Its goal is to maximize
        developer productivity and provide an environment where developers can
        focus on more creative tasks.
      </p>
      <p>
        In modern software development, there are many tasks beyond just coding.
        Code reviews, test creation, documentation generation, data
        analysisâ€”these repetitive tasks consume developers' valuable time.
        Claude Code Workflow Studio automates and streamlines these tasks
        through the power of AI, allowing developers to focus on more essential
        problem-solving.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Project Background</h2>
      <p>This project was started to address the following challenges:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Automating Repetitive Tasks:</strong>
          Automate routine tasks that are repeated daily to save developers'
          time
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Improving Code Quality:</strong>
          Consistent code reviews and best practice application through AI
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Knowledge Sharing:</strong>
          Share workflow know-how across teams and promote standardization
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Easing the Learning Curve:</strong>
          AI supports the learning of new technologies and frameworks
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h4>AI-Driven Code Review</h4>
          <p>
            Claude AI automatically analyzes code and provides suggestions for
            quality improvements.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h4>Data Analysis Pipeline</h4>
          <p>
            Automate data collection, transformation, and visualization to
            quickly gain insights.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h4>Automated Test Generation</h4>
          <p>
            Analyze your codebase and generate appropriate unit and integration
            tests.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h4>Documentation Generation</h4>
          <p>
            Automatically generate technical documentation from code and keep it
            always up to date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Customizable Workflows</h3>
      <p>
        Workflows can be flexibly customized to meet your project's needs.
        Integration with existing CI/CD pipelines is straightforward, supporting
        major platforms like GitHub and GitLab.
      </p>

      <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Claude AI:</strong>Leveraging natural language processing and
          advanced reasoning capabilities
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Astro:</strong>Fast and efficient static site generation
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>TypeScript:</strong>Type safety and improved developer
          experience
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>GitHub Actions:</strong>Continuous integration and deployment
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>Our Quick Start Guide will help you get up and running quickly.</p>
      <a href="/blog/002-quick-start-tutorial" class="cta-button"
        >View Quick Start Guide</a
      >
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
